{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887801590,"sessionID":"ses_284d8f87bffegEi2p0mTWPea3s","part":{"id":"prt_d7b27c0e8001G8Z7aUt3PFZ9Am","messageID":"msg_d7b27b8250014N7b73zxT2k4tt","sessionID":"ses_284d8f87bffegEi2p0mTWPea3s","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","content":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令\n\n> **AR ID:** AR-021  \n> **Module:** `cmd/cli`  \n> **Language:** Python  \n> **Size:** M  \n> **Stage:** ST-3 (Design) Completed → ST-4 (Implementation)\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `build` command builds a container image from the packaged agent workspace. It supports both local Docker builds and cloud-based build services. The command validates the workspace has been packed, loads metadata, determines the appropriate build strategy, executes the build process, and updates metadata with build results.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.1 — Build Models & Options\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.1.1 | Create `BuildOptions` dataclass in `agentcube/models/build_models.py` | Fields: proxy, cloud_provider, output, verbose; `from_options()` classmethod works | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.2 | Create `BuildResult` dataclass with build metadata | Fields: status, image_name, image_tag, build_timestamp, build_duration, logs_path | 0.5h |\n| 4.1.3 | Add `BuildStatus` enum (PENDING, BUILDING, SUCCESS, FAILED) | Enum values accessible; can serialize to string | 0.25h |\n| 4.1.4 | Update `agentcube/models/__init__.py` to export build models | BuildOptions, BuildResult, BuildStatus importable | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Build models defined and exportable.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.2 — BuildRuntime Core\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.2.1 | Update `BuildRuntime.__init__()` with MetadataService | Service instantiated; logger configured | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.2 | Implement `BuildRuntime.build()` main entry point | Returns BuildResult with all required fields | 1h |\n| 4.2.3 | Implement `BuildRuntime._validate_workspace_packed()` | Checks for agent_metadata.yaml; raises if not packed | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.4 | Implement `BuildRuntime._load_build_metadata()` | Loads metadata using MetadataService | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.5 | Implement `BuildRuntime._determine_build_strategy()` | Returns \"local\" or \"cloud\" based on metadata.build_mode | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.6 | Implement `BuildRuntime._prepare_build_context()` | Validates Dockerfile exists; returns build context path | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.7 | Implement `BuildRuntime._update_build_metadata()` | Sets build_timestamp, build_status, image info; saves metadata | 0.5h |\n| 4.2.8 | Implement `BuildRuntime._prepare_output_path()` | Returns Path; creates directory if needed | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** BuildRuntime core methods implemented.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.3 — Local Build Implementation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.3.1 | Implement `BuildRuntime._build_local()` dispatcher | Returns BuildResult; calls language-specific builder | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.2 | Implement `BuildRuntime._build_local_docker()` | Uses subprocess to call `docker build`; captures output | 1h |\n| 4.3.3 | Implement `BuildRuntime._generate_image_tag()` | Format: `{agent_name}:{version}` or `{agent_name}:latest` | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.4 | Implement `BuildRuntime._parse_dockerfile_language()` | Reads Dockerfile; detects FROM image to confirm language | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.5 | Handle Docker not installed error | Raises RuntimeError with clear message if docker command fails | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.6 | Handle Docker build failure | Captures exit code; raises BuildError with logs | 0.5h |\n| 4.3.7 | Save build logs to output path | Writes docker build output to `{output}/build.log` | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Local Docker build works end-to-end.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.4 — Cloud Build Implementation (Stub)\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.4.1 | Implement `BuildRuntime._build_cloud()` dispatcher | Returns BuildResult; validates cloud_provider | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.2 | Implement `BuildRuntime._build_cloud_huawei()` stub | Logs \"Cloud build not yet implemented\"; returns pending status | 0.5h |\n| 4.4.3 | Validate cloud_provider is supported | Raises ValueError if provider not in supported list | 0.25h |\n| 4.4.4 | Handle missing cloud credentials | Raises AuthenticationError if credentials not configured | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Cloud build stub implemented with proper validation.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.5 — Proxy & Network Configuration\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.5.1 | Implement `BuildRuntime._configure_proxy()` | Sets HTTP_PROXY, HTTPS_PROXY env vars for build | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.2 | Implement `BuildRuntime._get_docker_build_args()` | Returns list of --build-arg for proxy settings | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.3 | Pass proxy config to local Docker build | Docker build command includes proxy build args | 0.5h |\n| 4.5.4 | Validate proxy URL format | Raises ValueError if proxy URL is malformed | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Proxy configuration works for local builds.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.6 — CLI Integration\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.6.1 | Update `build` command in `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Remove \"not yet implemented\" stub | 0.25h |\n| 4.6.2 | Wire build command to BuildRuntime | Instantiates runtime; calls build(); handles errors | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.3 | Add Rich progress spinner during build | Progress indicator shown during build operation | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.4 | Format success message with image info | Prints image_name, image_tag, build_duration on success | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.5 | Format failure message with logs path | Prints error and logs location on failure | 0.5h |\n| 4.6.6 | Handle BuildRuntime exceptions in `_handle_error()` | Error messages displayed in red; traceback if verbose | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** CLI build command works end-to-end with proper UI.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.7 — Error Handling & Exceptions\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.7.1 | Create `BuildError` exception class | Inherits from RuntimeError; accepts message and logs | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.2 | Create `WorkspaceNotPackedError` exception class | Raised when agent_metadata.yaml missing | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.3 | Create `DockerNotFoundError` exception class | Raised when docker command not available | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.4 | Create `AuthenticationError` exception class | Raised when cloud credentials missing | 0.5h |\n| 4.7.5 | Add exception classes to `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` | All exceptions exportable from runtime package | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Custom exceptions defined and used appropriately.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.8 — Unit Tests — Build Models\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.8.1 | Write `TestBuildOptions` — creation with all fields | Options object created correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.2 | Write `TestBuildOptions` — from_options filtering | None values filtered; non-None values preserved | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.3 | Write `TestBuildResult` — creation with all fields | Result object created correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.4 | Write `TestBuildStatus` — enum values | PENDING, BUILDING, SUCCESS, FAILED accessible | 0.5h |\n| 4.8.5 | Write `TestBuildStatus` — serialization | str(status) returns expected value | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Model tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.9 — Unit Tests — BuildRuntime Core\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.9.1 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — initialization | Creates logger and MetadataService | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.2 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — validate workspace packed | WorkspaceNotPackedError if no metadata | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.3 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — load build metadata | Loads from agent_metadata.yaml | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.4 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — determine local strategy | Returns \"local\" when build_mode=local | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.5 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — determine cloud strategy | Returns \"cloud\" when build_mode=cloud | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.6 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — prepare build context | Returns path; validates Dockerfile exists | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.7 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — build context missing Dockerfile | Raises FileNotFoundError | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.8 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — prepare output path | Creates directory; returns Path | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.9 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — generate image tag | Format: name:version or name:latest | 0.5h |\n| 4.9.10 | Write `TestBuildRuntime` — update build metadata | Sets timestamp, status, image info | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** BuildRuntime core tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.10 — Unit Tests — Local Build\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.10.1 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — docker build success | Returns SUCCESS status; correct image tag | 1h |\n| 4.10.2 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — docker build failure | Returns FAILED status; captures logs | 1h |\n| 4.10.3 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — docker not found | Raises DockerNotFoundError | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.4 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — parse dockerfile language | Detects Python FROM image correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.5 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — parse dockerfile language Java | Detects Java FROM image correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.6 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — proxy configuration | Build args include proxy settings | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.7 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — save build logs | Log file created in output path | 0.5h |\n| 4.10.8 | Write `TestLocalBuild` — build duration tracking | Duration > 0 in BuildResult | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Local build tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.11 — Unit Tests — Cloud Build\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.11.1 | Write `TestCloudBuild` — unsupported provider | Raises ValueError for unknown provider | 0.5h |\n| 4.11.2 | Write `TestCloudBuild` — huawei stub returns pending | Returns PENDING status | 0.5h |\n| 4.11.3 | Write `TestCloudBuild` — missing credentials | Raises AuthenticationError | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Cloud build tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.12 — Unit Tests — CLI\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.12.1 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — default options | workspace=\".\", verbose=False | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.2 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — workspace override | -f /path/to/agent passed correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.3 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — proxy option | -p http://proxy:8080 passed correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.4 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — cloud provider option | --cloud-provider huawei passed correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.5 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — output option | --output /build/output passed correctly | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.6 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — error handling non-verbose | Prints error, no traceback, exit 1 | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.7 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — error handling verbose | Prints error + traceback, exit 1 | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.8 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — success output | Success message with image info displayed | 0.5h |\n| 4.12.9 | Write `TestCLIBuild` — failure output | Failure message with logs path displayed | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** CLI tests pass with >80% coverage.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.13 — Integration Tests\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.13.1 | Create `tests/integration/test_build.py` with fixtures | Temp directories with packed Python/Java agents | 1h |\n| 4.13.2 | Test complete Python local build workflow | Valid workspace → image built → metadata updated | 2h |\n| 4.13.3 | Test complete Java local build workflow | Valid workspace → image built → metadata updated | 2h |\n| 4.13.4 | Test build with existing metadata | Build info merged with existing metadata | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.5 | Test build with CLI proxy override | Proxy settings applied to build | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.6 | Test build failure — workspace not packed | Error message displayed, exit code 1 | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.7 | Test build failure — missing Dockerfile | Error message displayed, exit code 1 | 0.5h |\n| 4.13.8 | Test verbose mode output | DEBUG logs visible during operation | 0.5h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Integration tests pass with real filesystem operations.\n\n---\n\n## ST-4.14 — Documentation\n\n| # | Task | Verification | Est. |\n|---|------|--------------|------|\n| 4.14.1 | Add module docstring to `agentcube/models/build_models.py` | Clear description of build models | 0.5h |\n| 4.14.2 | Document `BuildOptions` fields with descriptions | Each field documented | 0.25h |\n| 4.14.3 | Document `BuildResult` fields with descriptions | Each field documented | 0.25h |\n| 4.14.4 | Add docstrings to `BuildRuntime` methods | Args, returns, raises documented | 0.5h |\n| 4.14.5 | Document exception classes | Purpose and usage documented | 0.25h |\n\n**Deliverable:** Code is well-documented for maintainers.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Phase | Tasks | Est. Hours |\n|-------|-------|------------|\n| ST-4.1: Build Models | 4 | 1.5h |\n| ST-4.2: BuildRuntime Core | 8 | 5h |\n| ST-4.3: Local Build | 7 | 4.5h |\n| ST-4.4: Cloud Build | 4 | 1.75h |\n| ST-4.5: Proxy Configuration | 4 | 2h |\n| ST-4.6: CLI Integration | 6 | 2.75h |\n| ST-4.7: Error Handling | 5 | 2.25h |\n| ST-4.8: Unit Tests — Models | 5 | 2.25h |\n| ST-4.9: Unit Tests — BuildRuntime Core | 10 | 5h |\n| ST-4.10: Unit Tests — Local Build | 8 | 4h |\n| ST-4.11: Unit Tests — Cloud Build | 3 | 1.5h |\n| ST-4.12: Unit Tests — CLI | 9 | 4h |\n| ST-4.13: Integration Tests | 8 | 7h |\n| ST-4.14: Documentation | 5 | 1.75h |\n| **Total** | **86** | **45.25h** |\n\n---\n\n## File Deliverables Checklist\n\n- [ ] `agentcube/models/build_models.py` — BuildOptions, BuildResult, BuildStatus\n- [ ] `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` — BuildRuntime implementation (updated)\n- [ ] `agentcube/runtime/exceptions.py` — BuildError, WorkspaceNotPackedError, DockerNotFoundError, AuthenticationError\n- [ ] `agentcube/cli/main.py` — Build command implementation (updated)\n- [ ] `tests/unit/test_build_models.py` — Build model unit tests\n- [ ] `tests/unit/test_build_runtime.py` — BuildRuntime unit tests\n- [ ] `tests/unit/test_cli_build.py` — Build CLI unit tests\n- [ ] `tests/integration/test_build.py` — Build integration tests\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Import verification\npython -c \"from agentcube.models.build_models import BuildOptions, BuildResult, BuildStatus\"\npython -c \"from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime\"\npython -c \"from agentcube.runtime.exceptions import BuildError, WorkspaceNotPackedError\"\n\n# CLI entry point verification\nkubectl-agentcube build --help\n\n# Unit test verification\npytest tests/unit/test_build_models.py -v\npytest tests/unit/test_build_runtime.py -v\npytest tests/unit/test_cli_build.py -v\n\n# Integration tests\npytest tests/integration/test_build.py -v\n\n# Coverage report\npytest --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing\n\n# Lint verification\nruff check agentcube/\nmypy agentcube/\n```\n\n---\n\n## Definition of Done\n\n- [ ] All 86 tasks complete\n- [ ] Build command works end-to-end (`kubectl-agentcube build`)\n- [ ] Local Docker build produces working images\n- [ ] Cloud build stub implemented with validation\n- [ ] Unit tests pass (>80% coverage for each module)\n- [ ] Integration tests pass\n- [ ] Type checking passes (`mypy`)\n- [ ] Linting passes (`ruff`)\n- [ ] Documentation complete with docstrings\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `docker` — Docker CLI must be installed for local builds\n- `typer[all]>=0.9.0` — CLI framework\n- `pydantic>=2.0.0` — Data validation\n- `pyyaml>=6.0` — YAML parsing\n- `rich>=13.0.0` — Progress indicators and output\n- `pytest>=7.4.0` — Testing framework\n- `pytest-cov>=4.1.0` — Coverage reporting\n- `pytest-mock>=3.11.0` — Mocking utilities\n\n---\n\n## Design Notes\n\n- **Build strategy:** Determined by metadata.build_mode (local/cloud)\n- **Local build:** Uses `docker build` subprocess with proper error handling\n- **Cloud build:** Stub implementation for future providers (huawei, aws, gcp)\n- **Image tagging:** `{agent_name}:{version}` or `{agent_name}:latest` if no version\n- **Proxy support:** HTTP_PROXY/HTTPS_PROXY passed as build args\n- **Build logs:** Saved to `{output}/build.log` for troubleshooting\n- **Metadata update:** Sets build_timestamp, build_status, image info\n- **Error handling:** Specific exceptions for different failure modes\n- **Workspace validation:** Requires pack to have been run first (agent_metadata.yaml)\n\n(End of file)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/cli/main.py":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775887801578,"end":1775887801587}}}}
